T02TD2078E:158b-1: aa lum bi ni pi sh'a tsi s'a dha nam /
T02TD2078E:158b-3: sha za aa lumbi ni'i sgrub thabs /
T02TD2078E:158b-4: aom lumbi ni bi lumbi ni sham sha pi sh'a tsa ni sv'a h'a /
T02TD2078E:158b-6: khyim stong bar nag po'i phyogs kyi tshes gcig nas mgal ba'i me byas te /
T02TD2078E:158b-7: las thams cad pa'i thab khung du rang gi khrag dang /
T02TD2078E:158b-12: thod pa dum bu lnga pa dang /
T02TD2078E:158b-13: ba glang gi khrag gis byugs pa'i seng ldeng gi so shing stong phrag gcig la bka' bsgo zhing gcer bur byas pas spyin sreg byas te mthong nas ma'am srid mor gyur te /
T02TD2078E:158b-14: nis ka bcu drug slong na brgyad ster ro //
T02TD2078E:158b-15: rang gi khrag dang chang bsres pas mo byung ba'i dus su mchod yon phul lo //
T02TD2078E:158b-16: aa lumbi ni zhes bya ba'i sgrub thabs rdzogs so//
